&lt;li&gt;This is a full time (40 hours&amp;nbsp;per week), non-exempt/hourly position.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This role includes&amp;nbsp;32 days&amp;nbsp;of scheduled breaks, 3 days of paid personal time off, 9 paid days of care (sick) time, 10 paid holidays, and&amp;nbsp;additional&amp;nbsp;time off if required by applicable law. Benefits for this role include medical, dental, and vision insurance, life insurance, disability insurance, a 401(k) plan with a 4% employer contribution match, an employer-matched flexible spending account for dependent care, and more. Please &lt;a href=&quot;https://day1academies.sharepoint.com/:b:/g/IQCuIl5IdYk7SY45rzPLI2poAcBo-a6bPiAyjGWMk9imO7s?e=HIB2Kv&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;see here&lt;/a&gt; for details.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
