&lt;li&gt;This is a full-time (35 or 40 hours per week), benefits-eligible, non-exempt/hourly position.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compensation for this position is &lt;strong&gt;$19-$27 per hour (~$39,000-$56,000 annually)&lt;/strong&gt;. The upper third of the compensation range is typically reserved for existing employees who have been in the role for multiple years and demonstrate strong performance over time. &lt;strong&gt;Starting compensation will vary with prior experience and qualification but is estimated to be $22-$25 per hour.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
